ectrum and\nequilateral bispectrum i.e. $P(k)-B(k, k, k)$ space.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Aug 2017 18:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 6 Feb 2018 14:34:09 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 23 Feb 2018 13:08:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-14"}
