r gas void location. Computer-simulated\nand experimental data are employed to demonstrate the effectiveness of the\napproach in mitigating artifacts due to acoustic heterogeneities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Aug 2017 20:57:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Sep 2017 14:59:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-08"}
