nphonon lifetimes and smaller Gr$\\mathrm{\\ddot{u}}$neisen parameters. Finally,\nthe total thermal conductivity as a function of temperature is predicted for\npristine ZrTe.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Aug 2017 07:54:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-17"}
