ally help (by a factor polynomial in $\\Delta$) in the global\nbroadcast. Therefore, unlike in the case of local broadcast, some additional\nmodel features may help in global broadcast.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Aug 2017 09:09:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 27 Oct 2017 08:10:07 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 10 Jan 2018 09:47:44 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 12 Jan 2018 13:54:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-15"}
