udy where all the phase\nnoises are assumed to be untrusted. We conduct an experiment to show the\nrequired phase stability can be achieved in a coherent communication system\nusing a true LO.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Aug 2017 13:46:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Dec 2017 19:38:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-16"}
